GLFW:
git clone https://github.com/glfw/glfw && mkdir build && cd build && cmake ../glfw && make -j4 && sudo make install
Get on Glad opengl and download the zip file
Install eigen
Build hdf5 and matio following the instruction on matio site, (remember to enable mat73)
Install OpenCTM (in the repo)
build assimp
Replace your library in the lib folder
